Usage: set_drive [-help] <resistance_value> <port_list> [-fall] [-max] [-min]
                 [-rise]

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<resistance_value>     # Value of the drive resistance (float, required)
<port_list>            # List of ports (string, required)
-fall                  # Specifies the drive resistance for falling transition
                       # (bool, optional)
-max                   # Specifies the drive resistance for late path
                       # (bool, optional)
-min                   # Specifies the drive resistance for early path
                       # (bool, optional)
-rise                  # Specifies the drive resistance for rising transition
                       # (bool, optional)